ol.li:
Parallelize the files in $GTFREE/prestable/converted/sme 
                and $GTFREE/prestable/converted/nob using this command: 


                for file in `find $GTFREE/prestable/converted/sme -name \*.xml | grep -v .svn`; 
                do corpus-parallel.pl --lang1=sme --lang2=nob $file ; 
                done
